title: Krooma Studio landing page
text: My first real job for a creative agency, animated with the 'AOS' library, some carrousels with 'Swiper' and 'react-responsive-carrousel' libraries, and fully functional contact form wich redirects you to the home page once you send it. Fully responsive. It was my first time working with a team, we use Figma for the design and Gitlab for the remotely work with branches. Sorry no code :( its confidential!
